  "title": "Mellow Citrusy Vietnamese Dates Noodles",
  "description": "A citrusy and indulgent Vietnamese dish featuring stoned dates, ferment-kimchi, and low-calorie-friendly ingredients, this noodle dish is perfect for a weeknight dinner.",
