  "instructions": [
    "Cook the rice noodles according to the package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the orange juice, grapefruit juice, fish sauce, lime juice, toasted sesame oil, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the cooked noodles to the bowl and toss to coat with the citrus sauce.",
    "In a small pan, heat the ferment-kimchi over medium heat until warmed through.",
    "Add the warmed kimchi to the bowl with the noodles and toss to combine.",
    "Stir in the chopped stoned dates.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the noodles hot, garnished with additional chopped dates and kimchi if desired."
  ],
